BT 1 0 0 1 0 43.6 Tm /F1 9.2 Tf 13.2 TL (This document is organized by programming task rather than by source-file order. Start with the quick recipes, then use the) Tj T* (call maps for exact signatures. The API index includes public operational functions and the methods that perform storage,) Tj T* (validation, execution, review, export, or observation. Passive dataclasses are introduced where programmers construct them,) Tj T* (but their repetitive value-only properties are not expanded into noise.) Tj T* ET
Q
